      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, i'll check for the pests. but i was also wondering about the soil itself... like if there's something actually happening down in the dirt. is it possible for something to be actively consuming the nutrients or interfering with how the roots work from underground? i've heard stories about soil being \"dead\" or having weird things going on in it.",
